beer.beer_description:
Temptress - a Brown Porter infused with cocoa and whole vanilla beans – is a luscious winter warmer that has garnered a cult following since release in 2008
This malt-driven beer is made extra special by the addition of Dutch cocoa and vanilla beans. The palate is complex with alluring chocolate, coffee and caramel underpinned by a hint of vanilla.
